sections.heading: Repealed.
sections.text:
History:Laws 2001, ch. 108, § 1; repealed by Laws 2013, ch. 115, § 31.

Repeals.— Laws 2013, ch. 115, § 31 repealed 15-11-1 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 2001, ch. 108, § 1, relating to building services division powers and duties, effective June 14, 2013. For provisions of former section,seethe 2012 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
